    <p>To ring your bell, hold your phone in front of you and give it a single quick forward rotation.</p>

    <div class="demo" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="demo__hand"></div>
    </div>

    <button class="button -block -gold -large">Got it!</button>
  </div>

  <div class="hide-text">
    <select id="freestyle-note-select">
      <option value="A3">A3</option>
    </select>
  </div>
</div>
